Participate actively in knowledge transfer sessions, shadow experienced team members during daily operations, and review relevant documentation and system architecture to build comprehensive knowledge of the mainframe environment (including key applications, tools, technologies, and infrastructure). Simultaneously, engage in team meetings, one-on-one discussions, and process walkthroughs to gain insight into team roles, collaboration dynamics, workflows, decision-making processes, ongoing projects, pain points, and current challenges. This immersion will enable effective contribution to the team and informed recommendations for improvements
